(4, 8, 'Heat Transfer Labels', '<p>Turn your designs into lasting impressions with our premium heat transfer labels. Made with eco-friendly materials, they bond directly to your garment, eliminating itchy tags and offering a smooth, comfortable feel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our advantages:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Vibrant colors and sharp details:</strong>&nbsp;Showcase your logo,&nbsp;artwork,&nbsp;or care instructions in stunning quality.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Durable and resilient:</strong>&nbsp;Withstand washing and wear,&nbsp;maintaining their vibrancy for years.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Flexible and versatile:</strong>&nbsp;Apply to a wide range of fabrics,&nbsp;from cotton to synthetics.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Quick and easy application:</strong>&nbsp;Use a heat press or iron for efficient application.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Sustainable:</strong>&nbsp;Made with eco-conscious materials,&nbsp;minimizing your environmental impact.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Elevate your brand with Carnival Offset Printers&#39; heat transfer labels. Contact us today!</strong></p>', 'gallery-1-2024-02-19-65d3431289c7b.jpg', '2024-01-24 10:08:55', '2024-02-19 12:16:20'),
(8, 11, 'ALL KINDS OF GARMENTS LABEL', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From brand statements to care instructions, garment labels tell a story beyond the fabric. Woven labels boast timeless elegance, while heat transfers offer vibrant designs. Printed labels deliver detailed information, and leather ones exude luxury. Care labels whisper washing wisdom, while size labels ensure a perfect fit. Composition labels reveal fiber secrets, and flag labels proudly declare origin. Each label, chosen with care, becomes an integral part of the garment&#39;s identity. They&#39;re not just tags, they&#39;re silent storytellers, whispering quality, authenticity, and personality - making every garment truly unique</p>', 'all-kinds-of-garments-label-2024-02-19-65d343ef46e15.jpg', '2024-02-19 12:05:03', '2024-02-19 12:05:03'),
(9, 12, 'Hang Tags', '<p>Hang tags are silent brand ambassadors, influencing customer decisions in fleeting moments. We don&#39;t just create <strong>eye-catching designs</strong>, we craft engaging stories. From <strong>premium materials</strong> to <strong>sustainable choices</strong>, we ensure your brand shines. Think beyond price tags: <strong>tell your story, highlight features, and connect with your audience</strong>, all on a tiny yet impactful stage. <strong>Let Carnival Offset Printers elevate your hang tags to brand storytelling powerhouses.</strong></p>', 'hang-tags-2024-02-19-65d344e951fff.jpg', '2024-02-19 12:09:13', '2024-02-19 12:09:13'),
(11, 16, 'OFFSET ITEMS', '<p>Offset paper reigns supreme for its diverse range of printing applications. Made for <strong>high-quality, cost-effective results</strong>, it shines in:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Brochures &amp; Flyers:</strong>&nbsp;Crisp graphics and text pop,&nbsp;leaving a lasting impression.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Magazines &amp; Catalogs:</strong>&nbsp;Vibrant and smooth,&nbsp;ideal for captivating visuals and product showcases.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Newspapers &amp; Books:</strong>&nbsp;Excellent ink absorption ensures clear,&nbsp;readable content.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Business Cards &amp; Invitations:</strong>&nbsp;Make a statement with professional presentations and elegant textures.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Packaging &amp; Labels:</strong>&nbsp;Enhance your brand with durable,&nbsp;customizable options.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Choose from <strong>uncoated varieties for a natural feel</strong> or <strong>coated options for glossy brilliance</strong>. Eco-conscious? No worries! <strong>Sustainable offset paper</strong> offers guilt-free printing.</p>', 'offset-items-2024-02-19-65d34866b1746.jpg', '2024-02-19 12:24:06', '2024-02-19 12:24:06'),
(12, 14, 'Silica Gel', '<p>Silica gel isn&#39;t just those little packets you find in shoeboxes. It&#39;s a <strong>moisture-absorbing powerhouse</strong> made from silicon dioxide. These transparent beads have a <strong>vast internal surface area</strong>, allowing them to trap and hold water molecules like tiny sponges.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Think of them as miniature dehumidifiers! They&#39;re used in everything from <strong>protecting electronics and medication</strong> to <strong>drying flowers and preserving food</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even cooler? <strong>Silica gel is reusable</strong>! Once saturated, simply heat it up to release the trapped water and it&#39;s back in action. Plus, it&#39;s <strong>non-toxic and eco-friendly</strong>, making it a safe and sustainable choice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So next time you see those little bead packets, remember, they&#39;re more than just filler &ndash; they&#39;re <strong>silent moisture-fighting champions!</strong></p>', 'silica-gel-2024-02-19-65d34c364d81e.png', '2024-02-19 12:40:22', '2024-02-19 12:40:22'),
(13, 9, 'Reflective Heat Transfer Label', '<p>Upgrade your apparel with <strong>visually striking and safety-enhancing</strong> Reflective Heat Transfer Labels. These labels boast:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Brilliant Reflectivity:</strong>&nbsp;Dazzle under headlights or streetlights,&nbsp;ensuring night-time visibility and safety.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Durable Design:</strong>&nbsp;Heat-bonded for&nbsp;<strong>long-lasting wear</strong>&nbsp;and withstands washing and abrasion.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Customizable Style:</strong>&nbsp;Available in&nbsp;<strong>various colors and effects</strong>&nbsp;to match your brand aesthetic.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Versatile Application:</strong>&nbsp;Ideal for&nbsp;<strong>apparel, sportswear, safety gear, and promotional items.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Eco-Friendly Options:</strong>&nbsp;Many labels use&nbsp;<strong>recycled materials</strong>&nbsp;for a sustainable touch.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Stand out, stay safe, and express your brand story</strong> with Reflective Heat Transfer Labels. Contact Carnival Offset Printers today!</p>', 'reflective-heat-transfer-label-2024-02-19-65d34ca57cd8f.png', '2024-02-19 12:42:13', '2024-02-19 12:42:13'),
(14, 10, 'Heat Transfer Highdency Label', '<h2>Heat Transfer High-Density Labels: Durable Impressions, Vibrant Designs</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Heat transfer high-density labels offer a premium solution for garment branding. Made with a specialized film, they provide <strong>exceptional durability</strong> against washing, wear, and abrasion. Their <strong>high color density</strong> allows for <strong>vibrant, intricate designs</strong> that truly stand out.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key benefits:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Long-lasting:</strong>&nbsp;Resists fading,&nbsp;cracking,&nbsp;and peeling,&nbsp;even after repeated washes.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Vibrant colors:</strong>&nbsp;Delivers crisp,&nbsp;detailed designs with a rich,&nbsp;saturated look.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Soft &amp; flexible:</strong>&nbsp;Comfortable on skin and adapts to garment movement.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Eco-friendly options:</strong>&nbsp;Available in sustainable materials to align with your brand values.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ideal for:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sportswear and activewear</li>\r\n	<li>High-end apparel</li>\r\n	<li>Children&#39;s clothing</li>\r\n	<li>Bags and accessories</li>\r\n	<li>Logos and branding applications</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Get noticed with the lasting impact of heat transfer high-density labels.</strong></p>', 'heat-transfer-highdency-label-2024-02-19-65d34e4452d0d.jpg', '2024-02-19 12:49:08', '2024-02-19 12:49:08'),
(15, 13, 'Barcode & Price Sticker', '<p>These unsung heroes silently work behind the scenes, bridging the gap between product and information. Barcodes, with their intricate black and white stripes, encode unique identifiers, allowing for efficient scanning and tracking. Price stickers, their colorful companions, clearly communicate the value of an item.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Together, they streamline inventory management, ensure accurate pricing, and facilitate smooth transactions. They may be small, but their impact is undeniable - from supermarkets to fashion boutiques, they are essential cogs in the retail machine.</p>', 'barcode-price-sticker-2024-02-19-65d34ee5caa29.jpg', '2024-02-19 12:51:49', '2024-02-19 12:51:49'),
(16, 15, 'Graphics Design Solution', '<p>We help businesses of all sizes <strong>capture attention, tell their story, and achieve their goals</strong> through impactful visuals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our expertise spans:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Logo &amp; Branding:</strong>&nbsp;Develop a unique identity that resonates with your audience.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Marketing Materials:</strong>&nbsp;Craft compelling designs for brochures,&nbsp;websites,&nbsp;social media,&nbsp;and more.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Packaging &amp; Labels:</strong>&nbsp;Make your products stand out on shelves with engaging packaging.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'graphics-design-solution-2024-02-19-65d34fb21a193.jpg', '2024-02-19 12:55:14', '2024-02-19 12:55:14');
